Package jdk.classfile.constantpool

Interface ClassEntry

All Superinterfaces:
ClassfileElement, LoadableConstantEntry, PoolEntry, WritableElement<PoolEntry>
public sealed interface ClassEntry extends LoadableConstantEntry
Models a CONSTANT_Class_info constant in the constant pool of a classfile.
